.TH restflow 1  "restflow 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
restflow \- RestFlow \- AI Agent Workflow Automation
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBrestflow\fR [\fB\-\-db\-path\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
RestFlow \- AI Agent Workflow Automation
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR \fI<DB_PATH>\fR
Database path (defaults to ~/.local/share/restflow/restflow.db)
.RS
May also be specified with the \fBRESTFLOW_DB_PATH\fR environment variable. 
.RE
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable verbose logging
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR [default: text]
Output format
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRtext, json]
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
restflow\-chat(1)
Start interactive TUI chat
.TP
restflow\-completions(1)
Generate shell completions
.TP
restflow\-run(1)
Run an agent directly
.TP
restflow\-agent(1)
Agent management
.TP
restflow\-task(1)
Task management
.TP
restflow\-daemon(1)
Daemon management
.TP
restflow\-skill(1)
Skill management
.TP
restflow\-memory(1)
Memory operations
.TP
restflow\-secret(1)
Secret management
.TP
restflow\-auth(1)
Authentication management
.TP
restflow\-config(1)
Configuration
.TP
restflow\-mcp(1)
Start as MCP server
.TP
restflow\-info(1)
Show system information
.TP
restflow\-claude(1)
Execute via Claude Code CLI (uses OAuth)
.TP
restflow\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
